{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-06_beg","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":13,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_st_08-04","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"R8-6","storyName":"战场，蔓延不止","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"塔露拉描绘的未来图景或许能打动霜星，却好像并不能说服爱国者。在一场与乌萨斯驻军的交锋中，塔露拉终于见识了爱国者的战斗。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-06_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-06","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":11,"next":13,"characters":["阿丽娜","塔露拉","霜星","爱国者","乌萨斯当地驻军"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":4,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":7},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"晖洁：","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"最开始成为感染者的时候，我过得浑浑噩噩的。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"我知道科西切想利用我做很多事，但总是在害怕，他究竟要我做什么？","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"他是不是打算用些什么手段，让我花这么多时间建立起的感染者通信网毁于一旦？","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"还是说，他打算让我分裂感染者，让他们分散成城市派和聚落派？","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"更可怕的一种情况是，他会不会打算让感染者成为新的军队，重新让乌萨斯走入战争？","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"我只能猜测。灰暗萦绕在我的头上，挥之不去。","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"但我只能向前走。","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"有个雪怪，似乎是叫佩特洛娃的，她昨天拿瘤奶炒了油籽，这做法真奇特。味道还挺有趣的。","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2b/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutry_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":23},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那件事......我想起来了。真快，这都过去两年了。","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"战士们传来传去的是真的吗，所以你真和她打了一架？听说你们把那个废弃城市都炸没了。","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"没那么夸张。传言总是会变得越来越匪夷所思......我只是把她的源石冰晶烧化了。","id":29,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"character","id":31},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":33},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#5","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"萨申卡，不准乱跑，会滑倒的！","id":35,"figure":["avg_npc_079",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#5","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"看他们这能够自在生活的样子。挺好的。","id":37,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这就是我的职责。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"没想到你会自告奋勇去教孩子们。","id":41,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我跟孩子的感情可比跟乌萨斯之间的感情好。你刚才说你把什么东西烧化了？","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"霜星的源石冰晶。她小队使用的一种法术装置，我猜。","id":45,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那可是......霜星，她肯定不服气。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"哈，没错。吐一口气的功夫，我就被她冻上了半边身子。","id":49,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"等我反应过来，她已经冲着我的脖子一冰刀砍过来了。","id":50,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我拦住了她的刀，嘶的一声，这把剑这么几年来头一次结了霜。","id":51,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"她大概也是第一次看到有人能把她的刀切出豁口......","id":52,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"啊，看得出你很乐意说这段事。你是不是还挺自豪的？","id":54,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"也没......好吧确实......呃，这个孩子，躲在牧栏后面的那个，她叫什么？","id":56,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"柳包芙。别在这偷听，柳巴！下节课我就读故事给你们听。","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"没错，就讲个灰色森林里的鬼魂故事吧......很可怕的故事！","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"去帮老师拿些木屑来，好吗？用篮子装。谢谢你。","id":60,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"之后呢？","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"霜星......阿丽娜，你也知道，这可是霜星。她的名字比我更早在西北冻原感染者术师间传开。","id":63,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我以为你不喜欢别人把你的名字说来说去。","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"如果有人拿这个名字去威胁别人，我当然不乐意。但要是战士们听到这个名字就想挑战我本人，那挺好。","id":67,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"和你不一样，霜星可不会接受什么挑战。这样想，你真的把她惹火了。","id":69,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"她是感染者里顶尖的术师，顶尖的那种小队指挥，也是感染者里最强的战士。","id":71,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......不要误会，我没冲着这个目标去。","id":72,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"可在很多人眼里，你们是有相像之处的。孩子们有的说想以后变得像霜星一样，也有的说想当你这样的英雄呢。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"停，停。我真的不喜欢这个词。你呢，阿丽娜，你又是怎么想的？","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"在我眼里每个人都不一样。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我总觉得你就是会这么说。","id":80,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"其实，我也不太知道霜星小时候过的是怎样的生活，她的教养很好，可能她过得还不错。","id":81,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可别让任何一个孩子经历我经历的这些。","id":82,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你也很有教养。","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我不愿意提这事。","id":86,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"......塔露拉，我们谁也不知道这片大地留给他们的遭遇，会不会比我们遇见过的更荒唐。","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"丧气话。","id":90,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这也是我想做老师的原因。","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我的“老师”可不是你这样子的。","id":94,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......我明白你的意思了。你是说霜星也许也......","id":95,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"谁知道呢。没有一个感染者的人生是相同的。","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"总之，和霜星争执过后，我就再也没敢在技巧训练上懈怠过。别说法术，剑术也是。这些我可都不能输给她。","id":99,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你和她打了一架我知道了，然后呢？","id":101,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"撑到她气消了，她才告诉我这事她不做主。","id":103,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那就只有一个人能做主了。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"就像你说的这样，是的。在我们这场斗殴结束后没过多久......","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......从城市的另一端走来了一个......","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......人。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"回想一下都那么费力？","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"应该说是第一眼印象太震撼，使得我只能想方设法挑一些词给你。","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"中午的阳光倾洒在他身上，居然照不化他身上淤泥一样的黑色。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我正和霜星说着我的计划，我说到我会联系上其他城市的感染者。","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我想要调集资金建造或者谋取小型的移动城市，我邀请他们加入计划......","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我看到他的影子。我说不下去了。","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"为什么停下？","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我可不那么有自信。","id":121,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你也会没自信？我从来没见你不自信过。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那可是......爱国者。","id":125,"figure":["avg_npc_078",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你没能说服他。","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"到现在都没有。","id":129,"figure":["avg_npc_078",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"后面的事你都清楚，在我和霜星那场“友善的研讨”之后，我们的队伍成功和游击队合流了。","id":130,"figure":["avg_npc_078",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"挺好的。再怎么说，在听说能和游击队一起走以后，我们这里许多感染者都很高兴。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这两年来我们过得比以前好，你的选择没有错。这回你是对的，塔露拉。","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可......我想，游击队并不是看重我和其他的感染者战士，只是他们......无法忽视和我们一起同行的其他感染者。","id":135,"figure":["avg_npc_078",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那更没必要丧气了。因为你也是这么想的。","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"但两年了。事情没有一点进展。","id":139,"figure":["avg_npc_078",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这样吧，塔露拉，你是从什么时候开始觉得爱国者不认同你的？","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"一年多前......在我们和游击队合流后不久。直到现在。","id":143,"figure":["avg_npc_078",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":144},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"character","id":146},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutry_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":147},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":148},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":149},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"这不可能。","id":151,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们甚至不知道冻原上还有多少感染者活在乌萨斯的混蛋统治下，在这时候和游击队说城市的那些感染者，太早了。","id":152,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们不是要抛弃冻原的感染者。否则我怎么会带他们一起走？","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们迟早有一天要回来。我们的目标是让乌萨斯，不，整片大地的感染者团结起来......","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"也许我们身处不同的地方，但是我们对自己境遇的不甘没有区别。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我在某座城市中的朋友把这种行为叫做“整合”。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"他呼吁感染者团结起来，自称“整合运动”，围绕同一个信念，抗议乌萨斯现在这种对感染者的残酷统治。","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们也应该找机会抗议一下冻原上乌萨斯士兵对矿场的压榨，这说不定能让他们痛改前非。","id":160,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"塔露拉，不说乌萨斯的百姓，我们只说军队，乌萨斯军是不会放过我们任何人的。","id":161,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"如果你去南方是为了“抗议”，那我们不如直接去找一个师团送命。","id":162,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"乌萨斯不是一块铁板。这是我们的机会。整合运动所要做的是传递信念，只是我看到了更多机会。我们还要传递一个信号。","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"什么信号？","id":166,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"“你们并不孤单。”","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"——","id":170,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你很清楚我们在冻原上只是会消耗自己的力量。我们需要走出冻原。","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我不决定这种事。","id":174,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你还不愿意决定这种事。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"如果离去的代价是死亡，我的性命除了能换一两条乌萨斯士兵的命以外也没什么用。","id":178,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"但我们身边的人呢？","id":179,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"塔露拉，你没有带兄弟姐妹在身边。我不会让他们送死。","id":180,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"不过我觉得那个是对的。","id":181,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"哪一个？","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"告诉感染者他们并不孤单。","id":185,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"在雪原上我们花了太多时间在一件事上。","id":186,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"找寻朋友。","id":187,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"但是，去联合城市的感染者？","id":188,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"看来从大城市来的青年确实更喜欢幻想一点。","id":189,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我还不想被你嘲笑，霜星。","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我不嘲笑你。你很强，你带着他们走了很长的路，和我们一样。","id":193,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"但向南方去就是种幻想。","id":194,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"游击队在壮大，但我们是感染者。","id":195,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们没剩下几年时间......而你的联合又需要多少年......","id":196,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"正因如此——","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialog","id":199},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"爸？","id":201,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"character","id":203},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"啊......","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"爱国者先生？","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","id":210},{"type":"text","text":"爱国者在篝火旁坐下。和塔露拉不断在脑海中模拟的场景一样，爱国者只是坐下，一言不发，注视着篝火。","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......","id":213,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"没事的。你继续说。","id":214,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"image","id":215},{"type":"dialog","id":216},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":217},{"type":"image","x":"50","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":218},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"50","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-50","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","duration":"20","block":"false","id":219},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"正因为我们不剩下多少时间了。","id":221,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"南方有丰产的田地，有适宜的温度，有四季变化，有新鲜的食物。","id":222,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"资源，教育，前景......","id":223,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"以及未来。","id":224,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"——未来？","id":225,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"霜星，我很可能知道你的想法。","id":226,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我的想法已经写在脸上了。我不知道什么叫做“未来”。","id":227,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"留给我们的时间确实不多，我们能够踏足的地方也不会有多少。","id":228,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"但感染者应该有未来。属于未来的感染者的，属于我们之后的人的。","id":229,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"霜星......我们给那些感染者找一个家。","id":230,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可以不被乌萨斯的感染者纠察队骚扰的地方，不被乌萨斯军队所包围的地方。","id":231,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"你也很清楚，带着感染者一起会让游击队的行动受阻。但我们不会放弃他们。","id":232,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"这将是条艰难的道路。","id":233,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":234},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"character","id":236},{"type":"image","id":237},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"至少，我们在死前创造的那些希望，是可以留给其他人的。","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"以及，如果我们推翻乌萨斯现在这个感染者制度......","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"一切都会改变。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们势单力薄。","id":244,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"如果你不是感染者，你会和我握手吗？","id":245,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那我们就从握手开始做起。","id":247,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......你说的这些，可能......","id":249,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"爸？你去哪？","id":250,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"已经够了。","id":253,"figure":["avg_npc_025_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"character","id":255},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":256},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":257},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#3","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"先生......","id":259,"figure":["avg_npc_078",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"哎。","id":261,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"别太在意。","id":262,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":263},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":264},{"type":"character","id":265},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2b/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutry_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"他可能只是在考虑。","id":270,"figure":["avg_npc_079",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那他也确实考虑很久了。","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"两年来，我和他的所有谈话也都只是关于队伍建设和接下来的安排。他从来没有一次问起我有关的计划。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，不管他是在嘲笑你还是在反对你——啊，我觉得他不太像是个会嘲笑别人的人——你都会等下去的。我有没有说错？","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_079",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"想走出冻原，我们不能没有游击队的力量。我会坚持。","id":277,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"因为他是冻原感染者的希望？","id":279,"figure":["avg_npc_079",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我以为你不会这么说。如果是你应该......不会这么说？","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我就是想知道你的想法。","id":283,"figure":"avg_npc_079"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......我想，是因为他才是那个冻原感染者团结的象征。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"这个象征是没办法被传递到下一代手里的。","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":287},{"type":"dialog","id":288},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"character","id":290},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":291},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":293},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":294},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$frontline_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_frontline_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":295,"musicid":1},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"起来！你还要在那呆到什么时候？","id":296,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你冻着我了，你这白兔子......！","id":298,"figure":["avg_npc_078",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"就算你那只是点小火苗，可不能连这点冷气都撑不住！","id":300,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"在你冰封这些乌萨斯人的武器时，你可不是这么说的。","id":302,"figure":["avg_npc_078",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"兄弟姐妹，撤退！让他们追！把矿场的守军引出来！","id":304,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#5","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"撑到盾卫支援我们就好！别放弃！","id":306,"figure":["avg_npc_078",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":307},{"type":"character","id":308},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":309},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":310},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"——快。快走。快点。游击队已经包夹过来了。","id":312,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你是怎么判断——等等。","id":314,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那几个奇怪的源石装饰品，是游击队布置的？","id":315,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"那是为我父亲设置的。","id":317,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"乌萨斯军没有再追赶我们了。他们似乎很忌惮那东西。","id":319,"figure":["avg_npc_078",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"等等，这是不是......是不是什么萨卡兹的东西？","id":320,"figure":["avg_npc_078",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"他的萨卡兹仪式。现在这两个，已经算是手头材料能做出来最好的了。","id":322,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"爱国者......爱国者在这里？","id":324,"figure":["avg_npc_078",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"你也说了，我们这支队伍被袭击是意料中的事。既然你说要在这里消灭这个连队，那光靠我们的小队当然是不够的。","id":326,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......敌人已经开始骚动不安了。","id":327,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"你见过我父亲战斗的样子吗，塔露拉......？","id":328,"figure":["char_1505_frstar_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":329},{"type":"character","id":330},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯当地驻军","text":"那......他......是他......你们怎么没说......没说他在这！","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯当地驻军","text":"撤退！撤退！！别管了，别管了！","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯当地驻军","text":"等等！他是从队伍尾部来的？那我们面前这些是什么？","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯当地驻军","text":"喂？喂？！说话！说话！！","id":336},{"type":"character","id":337},{"type":"dialog","id":338},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"......","id":341,"figure":["avg_npc_025_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"character","id":343},{"type":"text","text":"直至本地驻军向他发动猛攻前，众人面前矗立着的高大萨卡兹没有做出任何动作，没有发出任何声音。","id":344},{"type":"text","text":"但塔露拉仿佛听见冻原的北风中夹杂着哭叫，那是这片大地本身的颤抖，它的邪恶在温迪戈面前节节退缩。","id":345},{"type":"text","text":"爱国者站定，向冻原投出了手中长戟。","id":346},{"type":"text","text":"只懂如何吞食活物生命的阴郁天空忽地被刺出一个空洞。","id":347},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"image","id":350}],"characters":["阿丽娜","塔露拉","霜星","爱国者","乌萨斯当地驻军"]}